The paper deals with problems in discrete geometry and extremal combinatorics, which are typically covered by the arXiv sub-categories cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The use of formations and their width function also suggests a connection to numerical analysis, which is covered by the sub-category cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
